Name: Himeko
Desc: The one who repaired the Astral Express.\nTo witness the vast starry sky, she decided to travel with the Astral Express.\nHer hobby is brewing hand-made coffee.

1.Name: Childhood
1.Desc: After "Victory Rush" is triggered, Himeko's SPD increases by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

2.Name: Convergence
2.Desc: Deals <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> more DMG to enemies whose HP percentage is <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> or less.

3.Name: Poised
3.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

4.Name: Dedication
4.Desc: When Himeko's Skill inflicts Weakness Break on an enemy, she gains <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> extra point(s) of Charge.

5.Name: Aspiration
5.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

6.Name: Trailblaze!
6.Desc: Ultimate deals DMG 2 extra times, each of which deals Fire DMG equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of the original DMG to a random enemy.

100301.Name: Sawblade Tuning
100301.Desc: Deals Fire DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Himeko's ATK to a single enemy.

100302.Name: Molten Detonation
100302.Desc: Deals Fire DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Himeko's ATK to a single enemy and Fire DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> of Himeko's ATK to enemies adjacent to it.

100303.Name: Heavenly Flare
100303.Desc: Deals Fire DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Himeko's ATK to all enemies. Himeko regenerates <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> extra Energy for each enemy defeated.

100304.Name: Victory Rush
100304.Desc: When an enemy is inflicted with Weakness Break, Himeko gains 1 point of Charge (max <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> points).\nIf Himeko is fully Charged when an ally performs an attack, Himeko immediately performs 1 <u>follow-up attack</u> and deals Fire DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of her ATK to all enemies, consuming all Charge points.\nAt the start of the battle, Himeko gains 1 point of Charge.

100306.Name: Attack
100306.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

100307.Name: Incomplete Combustion
100307.Desc: After using Technique, creates a Special Dimension that lasts for <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> second(s). After entering battle with enemies in the Special Dimension, there is a <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> <u>base chance</u> to increase Fire DMG taken by enemies by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> turn(s). Only 1 dimension created by allies can exist at the same time.

1.PointDesc: After using an attack, there is a <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> base chance to inflict Burn on enemies for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).\nWhen afflicted with Burn, enemies take Fire DoT equal to <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak> of Himeko's ATK at the start of each turn.
Skill deals <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> more DMG to enemies currently afflicted with Burn.
When current HP percentage is <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> or higher, CRIT Rate increases by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.
